         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="0d101f13-6bd9-45bf-afc1-0fe0347ebcd5"/>
               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>URE-K 50% Description</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">URE-K 50% </content>cream is a potent keratolytic emollient which is a gentle, yet potent, tissue softener for skin and/or nails.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Each gram of <content styleCode="bold">URE-K 50% </content>cream contains:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">ACTIVE: </content>50% Urea in a cream base of:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">INACTIVES: </content>Mineral Oil, Stearic Acid, Water, Glycerin, Polysorbate 20, Sepigel 305, Phenoxyethanol, Acrylate Copolymer and Vitamin E</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20171020"/>
               <component>
                  <section>
                     <id root="61ae492b-c5b3-4de9-b1b5-73b1e34ee58b"/>
                     <code code="42229-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="SPL UNCLASSIFIED SECTION"/>
                     <title>CHEMISTRY</title>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Urea is a diamide of carbonic acid with the following chemical structure:</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>
                           <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM1"/>
                        </paragraph>
                     </text>
                     <effectiveTime value="20171020"/>
                  </section>
               </component>
